    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "After the discussion in today's meeting, should grpc_channel_create_insecure even exist? What would be the difference between grpc_channel_create_insecure and grpc_secure_channel_create passed the credentials object returned by grpc_fake_transport_security_credentials_create?\n"
